# GitHub Personal Access Token (optional)
# Without this token, the site still works — it falls back to hardcoded content.
# With a token, the site fetches live content from the obsidian-secondbrain repo
# via ISR (revalidates every 3600 seconds / 1 hour).
#
# Create a token at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# Scopes required: repo (if private) or public_repo (if public)
GITHUB_TOKEN=your_github_pat_here
